data.description: Open house Sat 1/20 from 1-3 pm. Embrace golf course living at its finest in this exquisite Woodlands residence, where the #17 tee box graces your backyard, offering unparalleled access and breathtaking views of the greens. This home boasts a thoughtfully designed layout with 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths conveniently located downstairs. The spacious living room, formal dining room, and a well-appointed eat-in kitchen create an inviting atmosphere for entertaining and daily living. As you ascend the staircase, discover two additional bedrooms, another full bath, and a versatile bonus room connected to one of the bedrooms. This flexible space opens up endless possibilities, whether it becomes a home office, a playroom, or a cozy retreat. Upgrades include newly installed windows throughout the home. Step outside into the expansive backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying the serene ambiance. The option to join the country club presents an opportunity for an enriched lifestyle with amenities, including the golf course, tennis courts, swimming pool, and a driving range. Experience the epitome of leisure and recreation right at your fingertips. Seize this rare chance to own a residence that combines the elegance of Woodlands living with the allure of a golf course lifestyle. Your perfect home awaits – schedule a showing today!
